WEBVTT

00:00:44.362 --> 00:00:49.137
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

00:00:49.650 --> 00:00:52.200
=Episode 15=

00:00:53.039 --> 00:00:54.000
From what I understand,

00:00:54.337 --> 00:00:55.637
Qin Gang treasures

00:00:55.637 --> 00:00:57.075
his daughter the most.

00:00:57.920 --> 00:00:59.920
I think we should go with the flow.

00:01:00.200 --> 00:01:01.119
Use this opportunity

00:01:01.439 --> 00:01:02.359
to make him confess.

00:01:05.012 --> 00:01:06.079
I'm just thinking

00:01:06.687 --> 00:01:08.806
whether he was behind Madam Li's death.

00:01:09.159 --> 00:01:11.280
That, we can investigate further,

00:01:11.550 --> 00:01:13.840
but now, we need to make him
hand over the formula.

00:01:14.325 --> 00:01:15.524
This is your chance.

00:01:21.087 --> 00:01:22.319
Kicking him when he's down.

00:01:22.680 --> 00:01:24.400
Sihai, you're quite ruthless.

00:01:27.120 --> 00:01:28.359
To achieve great things,

00:01:28.800 --> 00:01:30.159
one mustn't sweat the small stuff.

00:01:30.760 --> 00:01:31.599
To get revenge,

00:01:32.280 --> 00:01:34.359
we can use unconventional methods.

00:01:35.262 --> 00:01:36.187
I disagree.

00:01:36.920 --> 00:01:37.400
Understood.

00:01:40.159 --> 00:01:40.680
Dad,

00:01:41.000 --> 00:01:42.770
if you ask me,
this was all Ye Chen's doing.

00:01:43.280 --> 00:01:44.400
Why would he do this then?

00:01:45.760 --> 00:01:46.480
Aoxue,

00:01:48.439 --> 00:01:49.439
I won't let

00:01:49.920 --> 00:01:51.480
whoever did this off.

00:02:08.519 --> 00:02:09.439
Martial Uncle,

00:02:09.612 --> 00:02:10.532
my men

00:02:10.532 --> 00:02:11.225
failed you.

00:02:11.787 --> 00:02:13.186
That brat, Qin Gang,

00:02:13.186 --> 00:02:14.937
just kidnapped your wife!

00:02:26.639 --> 00:02:27.479
Churan!

00:02:32.225 --> 00:02:32.875
Are you alright?

00:02:33.719 --> 00:02:34.400
I'm fine.

00:02:35.960 --> 00:02:38.080
Mr. Qin just invited me over for a chat.

00:02:42.960 --> 00:02:43.680
Ye Chen,

00:02:44.280 --> 00:02:45.680
we should have a proper talk.

00:02:50.260 --> 00:02:51.625
Is this your so-called principle?

00:02:51.630 --> 00:02:53.390
What happened
to not dragging family into this?

00:02:54.080 --> 00:02:56.479
If I really wanted
to do anything to your wife,

00:02:56.479 --> 00:02:57.840
you wouldn't be seeing her now!

00:02:58.199 --> 00:02:59.759
Or maybe you're wary

00:03:00.120 --> 00:03:00.960
of my retaliation.

00:03:02.325 --> 00:03:03.199
You?

00:03:03.487 --> 00:03:04.120
Enough.

00:03:04.879 --> 00:03:06.159
I don't have time for this.

00:03:06.599 --> 00:03:07.240
Listen here.

00:03:07.639 --> 00:03:08.639
I had nothing to do

00:03:08.960 --> 00:03:11.120
with Madam Li's death at all!

00:03:11.400 --> 00:03:12.039
Also,

00:03:13.479 --> 00:03:15.280
I have another big project for your wife

00:03:15.879 --> 00:03:17.439
if you'll give me the antidote.

00:03:18.050 --> 00:03:19.805
Do you know
how important Aoxue is to me?

00:03:19.962 --> 00:03:21.802
I can give my all for her!

00:03:24.825 --> 00:03:25.945
Give me the formula then.

00:03:26.587 --> 00:03:27.587
I might consider.

00:03:30.039 --> 00:03:31.759
Didn't you just say you'd do anything?

00:03:36.312 --> 00:03:37.568
Alright, Mr. Qin.

00:03:37.900 --> 00:03:38.659
I was just joking.

00:03:39.120 --> 00:03:40.080
Ms. Qin's poisoning

00:03:40.080 --> 00:03:41.587
has nothing to do with me.

00:03:41.719 --> 00:03:42.875
If I wanted to hurt her,

00:03:43.319 --> 00:03:44.319
she'd be crippled

00:03:44.319 --> 00:03:45.400
in the ring.

00:03:45.750 --> 00:03:47.025
Why would I bother with all this?

00:03:51.587 --> 00:03:52.660
Take your wife and leave.

00:03:53.080 --> 00:03:54.520
Do you believe me

00:03:54.719 --> 00:03:55.875
or do you just have no choice?

00:03:58.120 --> 00:03:59.800
Although I don't have Aoxue's antidote,

00:04:00.200 --> 00:04:01.360
I can still save her.

00:04:02.590 --> 00:04:03.712
No need to trouble yourself.

00:04:04.587 --> 00:04:05.587
I'll tell you honestly.

00:04:06.120 --> 00:04:08.439
I've invited the miracle doctor,
Shi Tianqi.

00:04:08.960 --> 00:04:09.800
No matter what,

00:04:09.800 --> 00:04:11.639
I won't let anything happen to Aoxue.

00:04:12.039 --> 00:04:12.560
Fine.

00:04:12.862 --> 00:04:14.781
I wish her a speedy recovery.

00:04:15.362 --> 00:04:16.043
Sincerely.

00:04:17.360 --> 00:04:17.719
Oh right.

00:04:18.700 --> 00:04:21.000
The big project for my wife
you mentioned...

00:04:21.000 --> 00:04:21.479
Get lost!

00:04:27.837 --> 00:04:29.839
Ms. Xiao, I'll see you off here.

00:04:30.675 --> 00:04:31.587
I hope to work

00:04:31.587 --> 00:04:32.426
with you next time.

00:04:33.237 --> 00:04:34.008
Thank you, Mr. Qin.

00:04:34.690 --> 00:04:35.120
After you.

00:04:36.160 --> 00:04:36.800
Watch your step.

00:04:38.040 --> 00:04:38.759
Ye Chen?

00:04:40.800 --> 00:04:41.800
You've got nerve

00:04:41.800 --> 00:04:42.319
to come here!

00:04:42.319 --> 00:04:43.160
Alright, Dong.

00:04:43.839 --> 00:04:44.580
Mind your manners.

00:04:48.040 --> 00:04:48.360
Why you!

00:04:49.639 --> 00:04:50.360
Who is this?

00:04:50.530 --> 00:04:51.079
Oh right, Dad.

00:04:51.720 --> 00:04:53.279
This is Master Yu from Xuanji Hall.

00:04:53.879 --> 00:04:54.600
Yu Jinghai.

00:04:55.160 --> 00:04:56.120
Master Yu,

00:04:57.120 --> 00:04:57.600
welcome.

00:04:57.879 --> 00:04:58.319
Mr. Qin,

00:04:58.600 --> 00:04:59.839
I'm here now.

00:05:00.240 --> 00:05:01.639
Your daughter

00:05:02.040 --> 00:05:03.439
will be safe and sound.

00:05:04.560 --> 00:05:06.040
Thank you so much, Master Yu.

00:05:06.439 --> 00:05:07.639
Master Yu knows both medicine

00:05:08.240 --> 00:05:09.120
and the mystical arts.

00:05:11.439 --> 00:05:12.120
Qin Gang,

00:05:12.600 --> 00:05:13.720
didn't you just said

00:05:13.720 --> 00:05:15.480
you invited some miracle doctor?

00:05:16.000 --> 00:05:17.450
Why did a charlatan show up instead?

00:05:18.040 --> 00:05:20.040
Dr. Shi is elusive.

00:05:20.040 --> 00:05:21.439
He hasn't appeared just yet.

00:05:21.879 --> 00:05:23.279
So I invited Master Yu first

00:05:23.639 --> 00:05:24.839
to check on Aoxue's condition.

00:05:26.079 --> 00:05:28.759
You're in pharma
but believe this stuff?

00:05:29.120 --> 00:05:31.240
Our traditional culture
is deep and profound.

00:05:31.520 --> 00:05:33.079
Although one can't believe everything,

00:05:33.480 --> 00:05:34.639
I'm willing to try anything

00:05:35.399 --> 00:05:36.720
for Aoxue's sake.

00:05:39.480 --> 00:05:39.959
Master Yu,

00:05:40.360 --> 00:05:40.759
this way.

00:05:41.200 --> 00:05:42.448
I shall start then.

00:05:42.712 --> 00:05:43.225
Sure.

00:05:43.480 --> 00:05:44.040
Please.

00:05:44.150 --> 00:05:44.950
My disciples.

00:05:45.319 --> 00:05:45.879
Yes, Master!

00:05:49.040 --> 00:05:50.079
Bring the compass.

00:05:59.900 --> 00:06:00.680
Follow him quickly.

00:06:01.360 --> 00:06:01.839
Goodbye.

00:06:02.279 --> 00:06:03.160
Please excuse me.

00:06:03.319 --> 00:06:03.879
You may leave.

00:06:07.720 --> 00:06:09.759
That compass was pointed at me though.

00:06:11.279 --> 00:06:12.360
I think Mr. Qin

00:06:12.360 --> 00:06:13.639
is grasping at straws.

00:06:14.120 --> 00:06:14.920
Foolish.

00:06:28.639 --> 00:06:29.079
Mr. Qin,

00:06:29.360 --> 00:06:32.000
the malevolent energy
in this home is getting heavier.

00:06:32.199 --> 00:06:32.800
Pull this out.

00:06:32.800 --> 00:06:33.439
Get rid of it.

00:06:34.279 --> 00:06:36.600
If we don't subdue the demon soon,

00:06:36.879 --> 00:06:38.240
not only your daughter,

00:06:38.240 --> 00:06:41.312
but everyone in this house
may fall victim to it.

00:06:41.480 --> 00:06:42.040
Master Yu,

00:06:42.600 --> 00:06:43.319
please proceed.

00:06:46.560 --> 00:06:47.879
Can we stay and watch too?

00:06:49.325 --> 00:06:50.759
Hey, you're so thick-skinned.

00:06:50.759 --> 00:06:51.759
Why haven't you left yet?

00:06:52.120 --> 00:06:53.399
I just wanted to watch.

00:06:53.680 --> 00:06:54.590
I won't get in the way.

00:06:56.000 --> 00:06:56.737
Master Yu,

00:06:56.879 --> 00:06:57.639
let's begin.

00:06:57.879 --> 00:06:58.439
Okay.

00:06:59.480 --> 00:07:00.040
Disciples.

00:07:00.480 --> 00:07:00.879
Yes.

00:07:01.399 --> 00:07:02.680
Form

00:07:02.680 --> 00:07:03.199
the array!

00:07:13.079 --> 00:07:14.560
Water,

00:07:14.560 --> 00:07:16.839
to me!

00:07:35.879 --> 00:07:38.319
Talisman, to me!

00:07:49.199 --> 00:07:50.279
H... Here.

00:07:50.600 --> 00:07:51.040
Stop.

00:07:51.279 --> 00:07:53.199
This object is filled with evil energy.

00:07:53.839 --> 00:07:56.680
It's blocking
the Qin family's geomancy core.

00:07:56.879 --> 00:07:58.439
If we don't remove it soon,

00:07:58.439 --> 00:07:59.199
it will...

00:07:59.480 --> 00:08:00.079
Oh no!

00:08:02.399 --> 00:08:02.959
Paper, to me!

00:08:04.680 --> 00:08:05.600
Paper, to me.

00:08:05.600 --> 00:08:06.319
Paper, go.

00:08:06.319 --> 00:08:07.160
Paper, to me.

00:08:07.160 --> 00:08:07.879
Paper, go.

00:08:07.879 --> 00:08:09.000
Here and there.

00:08:20.160 --> 00:08:21.000
Sword, to me!

00:08:28.319 --> 00:08:30.100
Subdue the demon!

00:08:30.225 --> 00:08:30.800
Retreat!

00:08:31.839 --> 00:08:33.839
Where do you think you're going, demon?

00:08:38.120 --> 00:08:38.799
D... Dad,

00:08:39.080 --> 00:08:39.919
there's blood on it.

00:08:43.639 --> 00:08:44.200
It's bleeding.

00:08:50.720 --> 00:08:51.679
Master Yu, thank you

00:08:51.679 --> 00:08:52.840
for slaying the demon.

00:08:54.360 --> 00:08:56.120
You truly have great skill, Master Yu.

00:08:56.799 --> 00:08:57.679
But Ms. Qin

00:08:58.039 --> 00:08:58.960
isn't recovered yet.

00:09:04.240 --> 00:09:06.039
Behold, the deity!

00:09:38.639 --> 00:09:39.200
Aoxue!

00:09:39.679 --> 00:09:40.399
Are you alright?

00:09:42.400 --> 00:09:43.240
Ms. Qin,

00:09:43.840 --> 00:09:45.320
please sit up.

00:09:45.320 --> 00:09:46.050
Sit up?

00:09:49.960 --> 00:09:51.360
Ms. Qin, please stand up.

00:09:51.600 --> 00:09:52.240
Stand up?

00:09:54.360 --> 00:09:55.120
Jump.

00:09:55.960 --> 00:09:56.720
Aoxue!

00:09:58.080 --> 00:09:59.159
Watch out, Aoxue.

00:09:59.159 --> 00:10:00.200
Take it easy.

00:10:00.200 --> 00:10:01.120
Come down, Aoxue.

00:10:01.360 --> 00:10:02.039
Quickly.

00:10:02.120 --> 00:10:02.440
Here.

00:10:02.639 --> 00:10:03.960
You just recovered. Take it easy.

00:10:03.960 --> 00:10:04.759
Calm down.

00:10:06.039 --> 00:10:06.639
Master Yu,

00:10:06.840 --> 00:10:07.559
thank you so much.

00:10:08.080 --> 00:10:09.039
Don't thank me yet.

00:10:09.039 --> 00:10:10.039
I've only temperorily

00:10:10.320 --> 00:10:13.080
sealed the demon in her body.

00:10:13.679 --> 00:10:15.399
To remove it permanently,

00:10:15.399 --> 00:10:17.600
you'll need auspicious treasures.

00:10:17.600 --> 00:10:18.559
Like what?

00:10:19.720 --> 00:10:20.462
Like...

00:10:20.840 --> 00:10:22.575
the snow-white East Isles Spirit Jade,

00:10:23.000 --> 00:10:25.199
blood-red Westlands Fire Essence,

00:10:25.762 --> 00:10:27.802
shimmering Southern Sea Pearl,

00:10:27.875 --> 00:10:29.787
and pitch black Northern Abyssal Onyx.

00:10:30.087 --> 00:10:30.727
These will do.

00:10:30.825 --> 00:10:32.639
That's the four cardinal directions.

00:10:33.000 --> 00:10:34.360
W... Where on earth

00:10:34.919 --> 00:10:36.137
am I supposed to find them?

00:10:36.480 --> 00:10:37.537
The Treasures Pavilion.

00:10:38.010 --> 00:10:39.425
They will be auctioning

00:10:39.425 --> 00:10:42.146
one Southern Sea Pearl in two days.

00:10:42.412 --> 00:10:44.050
Although it's not as good

00:10:44.050 --> 00:10:46.912
as East Isles Spirit Jade,
Westlands Fire Essence,

00:10:47.399 --> 00:10:48.519
and Northern Abyssal Onyx,

00:10:48.519 --> 00:10:49.062
it will

00:10:49.120 --> 00:10:50.799
definitely work

00:10:50.799 --> 00:10:52.360
to expel the demon in Ms. Qin's body.

00:10:53.625 --> 00:10:55.320
That's such a coincidence.

00:10:55.320 --> 00:10:57.350
That's Ms. Qin's good fortune.

00:10:57.500 --> 00:10:59.559
Whatever she needs
just so happens to be for sale.

00:10:59.559 --> 00:11:00.625
What do you know?

00:11:08.275 --> 00:11:09.120
Master Yu,

00:11:09.600 --> 00:11:10.320
don't worry.

00:11:10.862 --> 00:11:12.301
I'll get that pearl

00:11:12.301 --> 00:11:14.212
no matter what it takes.

00:11:15.680 --> 00:11:17.159
You've seen Master Yu's divine power.

00:11:17.159 --> 00:11:17.840
Lie down.

00:11:18.440 --> 00:11:19.240
Now get lost.

00:11:21.480 --> 00:11:22.120
Master Yu,

00:11:23.320 --> 00:11:24.320
until we meet again.

00:11:25.960 --> 00:11:27.519
Let's go. Stop looking.

00:11:31.559 --> 00:11:32.679
That Master Yu

00:11:32.679 --> 00:11:34.519
seems like he's got some skills.

00:11:35.412 --> 00:11:37.133
He's quite good at putting on a show.

00:11:38.559 --> 00:11:40.400
Why didn't you expose him just now?

00:11:40.679 --> 00:11:41.679
Since he came prepared,

00:11:41.790 --> 00:11:43.723
he might be connected
to Qin Aoxue's poisoning.

00:11:44.240 --> 00:11:45.399
But Qin Gang has been fooled.

00:11:45.960 --> 00:11:47.759
He won't believe
whatever I tell him now.

00:11:48.679 --> 00:11:49.679
You're not

00:11:49.679 --> 00:11:51.120
going to let this go, are you?

00:11:52.000 --> 00:11:53.799
He's going
to Treasures Pavilion in two days

00:11:53.799 --> 00:11:54.900
for the Southern Sea Pearl.

00:11:54.925 --> 00:11:56.287
I'll expose that master then.

00:12:14.687 --> 00:12:17.175
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

00:12:17.262 --> 00:12:21.015
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

00:12:21.475 --> 00:12:26.412
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

00:12:26.575 --> 00:12:28.862
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

00:12:29.175 --> 00:12:31.855
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

00:12:32.925 --> 00:12:35.550
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

00:12:35.850 --> 00:12:38.862
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

00:12:39.062 --> 00:12:42.112
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

00:12:42.225 --> 00:12:45.187
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

00:12:45.455 --> 00:12:48.612
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

00:12:48.837 --> 00:12:52.587
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

00:12:52.587 --> 00:12:55.450
♪I belong to no one♪

00:12:55.512 --> 00:12:58.962
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

00:12:58.962 --> 00:13:01.637
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

00:13:01.637 --> 00:13:07.975
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪